
Crunchy Top Ham and Potato Casserole

2 lbs. frozen hash brown potatoes, thawed
2 cups cubed ham
2 cups sour cream
1 ½ cups shredded cheddar cheese
1 can cream of chicken soup, undiluted
½ cup melted butter
1/3 cup chopped green onions
½ teaspoon pepper
TOPPING
2 cups crushed corn flakes
¼ cup melted butter

In a bowl, combine the first 8 ingredients. 
Transfer to a greased 13 x 9 x2inch baking dish.  
Combine topping ingredients; sprinkle over the top.  
Bake uncovered, at 350 degrees for 1 hour or until heated through.  10 servings
